               <Scope>Other</Scope>
               <Impact>Reduce Maintainability</Impact>
	       <Note>This issue makes it more difficult to maintain and/or port the product, which indirectly affects security by making it more difficult or time-consuming to find and/or fix vulnerabilities.  It also might make it easier to introduce vulnerabilities.</Note>
            </Consequence>
         </Common_Consequences>
